{"tid":800492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國考古界大力吹奏古代狄人部落附近發現金字塔","createTime":"2018-08-31T02:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T03:08:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a7fad7caf6acee0fa5f68c0faa9f5b7c1da2fcca","tid":800492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-08-30/656/n02a00_p_01_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-08-30%2F656%2Fn02a00_p_01_02.jpg&h=4defa79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國古代也有金字塔！陝西省神木市的石峁遺址，近日再度成為海內外媒體的焦點，除日前出土約4000年前的骨製口弦琴，堪稱中國音樂史乃至世界音樂史上的重大發現外，石峁遺址擁有約70公尺高的金字塔，更是讓外媒嘖嘖稱奇，並被視為中華文明探源工程「石破天驚」的重大發現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「皇城台就是中國的金字塔」，陝西省考古研究院院長、石峁遺址考古領隊孫周勇先前就曾以「石破天驚」，來形容此一中國已知規模最大的史前城址。而皇城台正是石峁遺址的核心區域，台頂約8萬平方公尺，除「猶如巍峨的階梯式金字塔」外，並分布著成組的宮殿、池苑等建築。<br />\n<br />\n石峁遺址日前也出土約4000年前的骨製口弦琴，為中國已知年代最早的弦樂器，再度印證其「在中華文明探源工程中占據著舉足輕重的位置」。至於「石峁甚至可能是黃帝部族的都邑」的說法，孫周勇認為，只是把古人遺存的文物與歷史傳說中的人物進行直接、簡單的比對，「目前還缺乏直接證據、為時尚早。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180830000109-260301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20180830000109-260301&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=525ca319\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180830000109-260301</a>"},{"pid":"b54793b6f5744ec14c811a5889da300868b25a3d","tid":800492,"uid":64191,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"唔係響中原發掘既都叫中華文明架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4019a47077c5327af692c1b2212ec11bff58a276","tid":800492,"uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"金字塔呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e22d6dd4668d9e857ca1624279a4a69c8d9b1b","tid":800492,"uid":77788,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdd67fb6d1bbaa7199d168d49b77ac34b5663a8a","tid":800492,"uid":13663,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:28:32.000Z","msg":"入面有冇寫叫刁種做皇帝"},{"pid":"840c4e77c90a53d46e1b329b72174a79e946f6bc","tid":800492,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"金字塔？<br />\n<br />\n即係證明左「中華文明西來說」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa17c84a147a6ab5965c2b4afbdd300e0350be4","tid":800492,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來埃及都是中國的"},{"pid":"a31476bc7a7e69ff7ccac96f32e9e5825c8ce894","tid":800492,"uid":61660,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"840c4e77c90a53d46e1b329b72174a79e946f6bc","tid":800492,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"金字塔？<br />\n<br />\n即係證明左「中華文明西來說」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得金字塔式建築係某個文明獨有"},{"pid":"7718d867168f874a506cd98a4df8ade29a12232b","tid":800492,"uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1aa17c84a147a6ab5965c2b4afbdd300e0350be4","tid":800492,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來埃及都是中國的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"美洲大陸都有金字塔，所以自古以來成個美洲都係中國不可分割的一部份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d438ef53f1fdb07a9cb19d61710ea87a080a7f4a","tid":800492,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a31476bc7a7e69ff7ccac96f32e9e5825c8ce894","tid":800492,"uid":61660,"like":2,"disl